Package: wrathos-bundle-steam
Version: 1.0
Architecture: amd64
Section: misc
Priority: optional
Maintainer: WrathOS Project <zxd@lunarys.org>
Depends: wrathos-base, flatpak, libvulkan1, libvulkan1:i386, mesa-vulkan-drivers, mesa-vulkan-drivers:i386
Description: WrathOS Steam bundle
 Installs Flatpak and Vulkan libraries needed for Steam.
 Steam itself is installed via Flatpak after package install.
